data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse boasts modern luxury and spacious living. With a 2-car garage, it offers convenience and storage space. The thoughtful design includes two primary bedrooms, one on each floor, providing flexibility and privacy for residents. The downstairs area features elegant ceramic tile flooring, which adds both style and easy maintenance. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a central island and an electric range stove for culinary creativity. Outside, serene water-front view awaits, creating a tranquil backdrop for relaxation and entertainment.  Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying quiet moments, this townhouse offers the ideal blend of comfort and sophistication in a beautiful waterfront setting.
